About Event

​Tired of the tedious tasks that eat up your planning time? This exclusive session is your entry point to AI literacy. Learn exactly how AI tools can drastically cut down on grading, lesson planning, and communication, giving you back hours every week. Don't be replaced by AI—learn to leverage it to become the most efficient and effective educator in the room.

​Unlocking AI Literacy for Educators (12:00 - 2:30 PM)

​Network/Food: 12:00 - 12:30

​Presentation 12:30 - 1:00 AI in Educ
